Surf_Tronia

by Sangre Nueva

Skill Surf Map

made for 66tick

Map Includes:

    4 Stages (Tier 3)

    4 Bonuses (with Overlay mode)

    

 Map Description:

-Map is made for Servers with Surftimer so there is no Jail or Maptimer  -All Stages are connected to each other (Continous Surf) with different Endings..(easy+slow/hard+fast)
-Bonus entrys arent obvious.. you have to explore the Map

Enjoy the Map !

-Sangre

Special thx to Untouchable for helping me fixing bugs and hosting the beta
